The sky is not the limit

Discover our Services.

Nothing is too much when it comes to service. Ship, barge, plane, train, truck, or multimodal transport. For you, we move mountains. Discover our logistics solutions.

What Makes us

Different?

Nothing great was ever achieved without enthusiasm

Having a positive and energetic attitude towards work and life contributes to a more productive and enjoyable work environment that helps to inspire creativity, innovation, and success.

Our global management is very accessible and approachable, which makes our communication style open and honest. We operate with an open-door policy, and you can take this quite literally.

Knowledge is Power

We are continuously focused on innovation and getting better every day. Because we work in a dynamic environment and our organization is growing, your development will grow together with MPL. We aim to bring out the best in ourselves and each other by sharing our knowledge and offering training and courses. You will find yourself in an environment with an international character and various opportunities worldwide.

Empowering people in a sustainable and enthusiastic culture to provide logistics services in a different way
Winners find a reason, losers an excuse

Responsibility, entrepreneurial spirit, and determination are core beliefs within our company. At MPL, we inspire excellence and stimulate continuous improvement. We do this by taking ownership of, and accepting accountability for, our actions and results.

You always meet twice

Maintaining honesty, transparency, and authenticity in all interactions. These values build trust, strong relationships, and a reputation for reliability, benefiting both our team and our customers.

Zero Bullshit

At MPL, we're all about delivering the real deal; there's no smoke and mirrors. We are committed to providing services that are straightforward, transparent, and results-driven.

Comprehensive Export Solutions

Across the globe, our teams are committed to fulfilling your export requirements. As a member of the RTM Group, we harness group resources to enhance our solutions, offering both financial stability and flexibility, all for your advantage.
